STEP 0: (For the impatient)
---------------------------------------------------------------
modify bootstrap-notau.sh as necessary, and run it.

STEP 1: Configuring and building APEX for HPX:
---------------------------------------------
(starting in the apex directory, the root of this tarball)

mkdir build
cd build
export BOOST_ROOT=/usr/local/packages/boost/1.55.0  (or equivalent)
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=. ..
   (or)
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=. ..
make
make test
make install

Precursor: Building BOOST:
------------------------
BOOST 1.55.0
./bootstrap.sh
./b2


